---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro'
import { site } from '../lib/site'
---

<Page title="CV · Serina McFall" description="Curriculum vitae for Serina McFall: software developer, accessibility-first, Auckland-based.">
  <article class="cv">
    <p class="download-bar">
      <a href="/serina-mcfall-cv.pdf" download="Serina McFall CV July 2026.pdf" class="download-btn">
        Download CV (PDF)
      </a>
    </p>
    <div class="cv-layout">
      <aside class="cv-sidebar">
        <h1>Serina McFall</h1>
        <p class="role">Software Developer</p>
        <p class="role-sub">accessibility-first · neurospicy</p>
        <ul class="contact">
          <li><a href={site.url}>vixenz.dev</a></li>
          <li><a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a></li>
          <li><a href="tel:+64214672266">+64 21 467 266</a></li>
          <li><a href={site.github}>GitHub</a></li>
          <li><a href={site.linkedin}>LinkedIn</a></li>
          <li>{site.location}</li>
          <li>NZ Citizen</li>
        </ul>
      </aside>

      <div class="cv-body">

 <section>
  <h2>Summary</h2>
  <p>Software Developer. Shifted from nearly a decade in customer service to a career in tech via Dev Academy. Server-side gives structure to the part of my brain that needs it; the front end gives an outlet to my artistic side. I found the home I did not know I was looking for. Neurodivergent, and I've learned this is not a weakness but is in fact a strength I can use. I plan and doc before I write code, gate accessibility up front (WCAG 2.2 AA) on my own projects, and start Dev Academy's AI Launchpad on 27 July 2026.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Experience</h2>

  <article class="job">
    <h3>Dev Academy Aotearoa</h3>
    <p class="job-meta">Auckland, NZ (Hybrid) <span aria-hidden="true"> · </span> Apr 2026 to Present</p>

    <div class="role">
      <h4>Software Developer <span class="role-dates">Apr 2026 to Present</span></h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Shipped three solo projects: Moonlit Library (deployed on Render), Atlas (accessibility-first concept library reworked from the bootcamp brief), and vixenz.dev (portfolio site, Astro on Cloudflare Pages).</li>
        <li>Accessibility-first on every project: WCAG 2.2 AA audits before merge, keyboard navigation + ARIA + focus management wired in from the start. Gave cohort lightning talk on treating accessibility as a design decision, not decoration.</li>
        <li>Learned to work with Claude Code as a coding partner and code reviewer: how to direct AI, question its output, verify what it ships.</li>
        <li>Passed all 11 assessment credentials, several ahead of deadline.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="job">
    <h3>Bachcare, The Holiday Home Company</h3>
    <p class="job-meta">Auckland, NZ (Hybrid) <span aria-hidden="true"> · </span> Dec 2021 to Apr 2026</p>

    <div class="role">
      <h4>Feedback and Owner Operations Specialist <span class="role-dates">promoted through Booking Management and Reservations Specialist</span></h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Owned guest feedback resolution across a 4.5-year progression, sitting between guest needs and owner constraints to land solutions that worked for both.</li>
        <li>Trained new team members on feedback methodology: what the role actually involves, and how to stay empathetic to guests who are frustrated.</li>
        <li>Supported the owner relations team day to day: maintenance escalations, guidance for owners, general problem-solving.</li>
        <li>Earlier in tenure: managed in-stay needs (maintenance, changes, cancellations) and complex bookings; ran pre-stay support and property matching.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="job">
    <h3>TIC Group</h3>
    <p class="job-meta">Auckland, NZ (On-site) <span aria-hidden="true"> · </span> May 2018 to Dec 2021</p>

    <div class="role">
      <h4>Claims Coordinator</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Ran the warranty claims lifecycle for JB Hi-Fi's faulty products: raised claims, handled supplier paperwork, saw them through to settlement.</li>
        <li>Owned salvage operations for TIC's NZ division: ordered containers, built picklists, coordinated pickup and shipping to the Auckland port for hardware bound for AU parts resale.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="job">
    <h3>JB Hi-Fi</h3>
    <p class="job-meta">Auckland (Sylvia Park, then Botany) <span aria-hidden="true"> · </span> Nov 2010 to May 2018</p>

    <div class="role">
      <h4>Counter Coordinator <span class="role-dates">promoted from Customer Service Representative, 4.5 years as Coordinator</span></h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Led the counter team of 5 for 4.5 years at Botany: schedules, one-on-ones, escalation liaison between team and management.</li>
        <li>Joined Sylvia Park on opening day (2010) and transferred to Botany in 2012; travelled to Christchurch for a week to help open that store on the strength of Sylvia Park launch experience.</li>
        <li>Counter operations throughout: sales, POS, cash handling, finance applications, returns coordination with distributors.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Projects</h2>
  <ul class="projects">
    <li>
      <h3>Moonlit Library</h3>
      <p class="project-meta">
        <a href="https://moonlit-library.onrender.com">moonlit-library.onrender.com</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true"> · </span>
        <a href="https://github.com/serina-mcfall/moonlit-library">github.com/serina-mcfall/moonlit-library</a>
      </p>
      <p><strong>Stack:</strong> Express + Knex + SQLite on the server and React + Vite on the client</p>
      <p><strong>Role:</strong> Solo build</p>
      <p><strong>Outcome:</strong> Dev Academy challenge, earned three credentials. Personal library designed for how I read, deployed on Render.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>Atlas: a visual concept library</h3>
      <p class="project-meta">
        <a href={`${site.url}/work/atlas`}>vixenz.dev/work/atlas</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true"> · </span>
        <a href="https://github.com/serina-mcfall/atlas">github.com/serina-mcfall/atlas</a>
      </p>
      <p><strong>Stack:</strong> React + Vite + TypeScript, Express + Knex + SQLite, MDX</p>
      <p><strong>Role:</strong> Solo build (in progress)</p>
      <p><strong>Outcome:</strong> Reworked a Dev Academy art-gallery brief into an accessibility-first concept library with kind-based routing. WCAG 2.2 AA gated in Playwright tests. Four concept sheets and a Terminal reference sheet shipped.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>Kiwicom: a developer project discovery hub</h3>
      <p class="project-meta">
        <span class="deploy-note">not yet deployed</span>
        <span aria-hidden="true"> · </span>
        <a href="https://github.com/Oscar-Wakefield-Ngahuru-2026/Kiwicom">github.com/Oscar-Wakefield-Ngahuru-2026/Kiwicom</a>
      </p>
      <p><strong>Stack:</strong> React + Vite + TS + Tailwind, Node + Express + TS, PostgreSQL (Supabase auth), Knex</p>
      <p><strong>Role:</strong> My role in this project was the git keeper of a 4-person team. I reviewed every PR, ran merges to Dev, and Resolved conflicts when they came about (luckily there were not many). 79 commits by the end, highest on the team.</p>
      <p><strong>Outcome:</strong> Final Dev Academy group project. Community hub for devs to find open-source projects: GitHub pulls filtered by language/topic, bookmarks, profiles, create-project. Editorial design system (Lexend + JetBrains Mono, cream and deep-sky) from my aesthetic. Claude-powered summaries + deployment planned but did not land in time.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>Realmstack</h3>
      <p class="project-meta">
        <span class="deploy-note">not deployed</span>
        <span aria-hidden="true"> · </span>
        <a href="https://github.com/Realmstacks/Realmstack">github.com/Realmstacks/Realmstack</a>
      </p>
      <p><strong>Stack:</strong> Cloudflare Workers (planning to bind D1, KV, R2, Queues), TypeScript. Rest of the stack still to be decided.</p>
      <p><strong>Role:</strong> Co-built with my husband. Currently in doc-led planning phase.</p>
      <p><strong>Outcome:</strong> Long-term worldbuilding platform for writers, D&amp;D masters, and game writers. Doc-led planning phase: north-star vision, user flows, and multi-source encryption architecture research (Claude, ChatGPT, Gemini, Kimi, Deepseek) locked before implementation. Client-side E2EE is the technical anchor.</p>
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Skills</h2>
  <dl class="skills">
    <div>
      <dt>Core</dt>
      <dd>
        <ul class="skill-list">
          <li>React</li>
          <li>TypeScript / JavaScript</li>
          <li>Node + Express</li>
          <li>Knex + SQL (SQLite, Postgres)</li>
          <li>HTML + CSS</li>
          <li>WCAG 2.2 AA + W3C APG patterns</li>
          <li>Playwright + axe-core</li>
          <li>Git</li>
          <li>Astro</li>
          <li>Vite + Vitest</li>
        </ul>
      </dd>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dt>Familiar</dt>
      <dd>
        <ul class="skill-list">
          <li>Tailwind CSS</li>
          <li>Cloudflare Pages</li>
          <li>Supabase (Auth + hosted Postgres)</li>
          <li>MDX</li>
        </ul>
      </dd>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dt>Learning next</dt>
      <dd>
        <ul class="skill-list">
          <li>Cloudflare Workers (D1, KV, R2, Queues)</li>
          <li>Agentic workflows</li>
          <li>Anthropic + OpenAI APIs</li>
          <li>Client-side E2EE</li>
        </ul>
      </dd>
    </div>
  </dl>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Education</h2>

  <article class="edu">
    <h3>Dev Academy Aotearoa</h3>
    <p class="edu-meta">Auckland, NZ <span aria-hidden="true"> · </span> 2026</p>
    <p>Full-stack web development bootcamp + AI Launchpad.</p>
  </article>

  <article class="edu">
    <h3>Emily Carr University of Art and Design</h3>
    <p class="edu-meta">Vancouver, BC, Canada <span aria-hidden="true"> · </span> 1998 to 1999</p>
    <p>Foundations Program (1 year, not completed).</p>
  </article>

  <article class="edu">
    <h3>North Delta Senior Secondary</h3>
    <p class="edu-meta">North Delta, BC, Canada <span aria-hidden="true"> · </span> Graduated 1998</p>
  </article>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Interests</h2>
  <p>Art in its many forms is my safe place: painting, digital art, Diamond dots, resin. Writing and worldbuilding sit alongside; D&amp;D and Magic the Gathering scratch the same itch. Current game obsession: Where Winds Meet. Reading, Chinese and Korean Dramas.</p>
</section>

<section class="references">
  <h2>References</h2>
  <p>Available upon request.</p>
</section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Page>

<style>

  .cv {
    max-width: 48rem;

  }

  .download-bar {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .cv-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 15rem 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .cv-sidebar {
    color: var(--mist);
  }

  .cv-sidebar h1 {
    font-size: 1.55rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--moonlight);
    margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .cv-sidebar .role {
    color: var(--magnolia);
    font-size: var(--text-ui);
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
  }

  .cv-sidebar .role-sub {
    color: var(--mist);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .cv-sidebar .contact {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    text-align: left;
    font-size: var(--text-ui);
    color: var(--mist);
  }

  .cv-sidebar .contact li {
    max-width: none;
  }

  .cv-sidebar .contact a {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 3px 0;
    color: var(--moonlight);
  }

  @media (max-width: 42rem) {
    .cv-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .cv-sidebar .contact {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .scaffold-note {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-ui);
    color: var(--mist);
    opacity: 0.65;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--tile-border);
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .download-btn {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-ui);
    color: var(--moonlight);
    background: var(--surface-card);
    backdrop-filter: blur(var(--surface-card-blur));
    padding: 0.5rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: box-shadow 200ms ease, transform 200ms ease;
  }

  .download-btn:hover,
  .download-btn:focus-visible {
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(232, 180, 196, 0.35);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .download-btn:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--magnolia);
    outline-offset: 4px;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .download-btn {
      transition: none;
    }
    .download-btn:hover,
    .download-btn:focus-visible {
      transform: none;
    }
  }

  .cv-head {
    display:flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--tile-border);
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;

  }

  .cv-head h1 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;

  }

  .role {
    color: var(--mist);
    font-size: var(--text-ui);


  }

  .contact {
    list-style: none;
    text-align: right;
    font-size: var(--text-ui);
    color: var(--mist);

  }

  .contact a {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 4px 0;
}

  .cv .projects, .cv .other {
    list-style: none;
    display:grid;
    gap: 1.25rem;

  }

  .cv .projects li, .cv .other li {
    color: var(--mist);
    max-width: none;

  }

  .cv .projects h3 {
    color: var(--moonlight);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
  }

  .cv .project-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    color: var(--mist);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .cv .project-meta .deploy-note {
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  .cv .projects p {
    margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .cv .projects p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .cv .projects strong {
    color: var(--lotus);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-right: 0.25rem;
  }

  .cv section {
    margin: 1.25rem 0;

  }

  .cv h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    color: var(--lotus);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
  }

  .cv .job {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cv .job:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .cv .job h3 {
    color: var(--moonlight);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.15rem;
  }

  .cv .job-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    color: var(--mist);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .cv .role {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    padding-left: 0.75rem;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--tile-border);
  }

  .cv .role:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .cv .role h4 {
    color: var(--moonlight);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .cv .role-dates {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    color: var(--mist);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .cv .role ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .cv .role li {
    color: var(--mist);
    max-width: none;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .cv .role li::before {
    content: "·";
    color: var(--lotus);
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .cv .edu {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cv .edu:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .cv .edu h3 {
    color: var(--moonlight);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.15rem;
  }

  .cv .edu-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    color: var(--mist);
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .cv .edu p:last-child {
    color: var(--mist);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .cv dl {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .cv dl div {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 10rem 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .cv dt {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    color: var(--lotus);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .cv dd {
    color: var(--moonlight);
    max-width: none;
  }

  .cv .skill-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: inline;
  }

  .cv .skill-list li {
    display: inline;
    color: var(--moonlight);
  }

  .cv .skill-list li:not(:last-child)::after {
    content: " · ";
    color: var(--lotus);
    padding: 0 0.15rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 36rem) {
    .cv-head { flex-direction: column; }
    .contact { text-align: left; }
    .cv dl div { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media print {
    .download-bar,
    .scaffold-note {
      display: none !important;
    }
    :global(.atmosphere) {
      display: none !important;
    }
    :root {
      --midnight: #ffffff;
      --moonlight: #1a1a1a;
      --mist: #444;
      --lotus: #444;
      --lantern: #444;
      --magnolia: #444;
      --tile-border: #ccc;
      --deep-sky: #ffffff;
    }
    :global(body) {
      background: white !important;
      color: black !important;
      font-size: 8pt;
      line-height: 1.28;
    }
    @page {
      margin: 10mm 12mm;
    }
    :global(body > .content-layer > header),
    :global(body > .content-layer > footer),
    :global(.skip-link) {
      display: none !important;
    }
    :global(body > .content-layer),
    :global(.page-inner) {
      background: white !important;
      padding: 0 !important;
      max-width: 100% !important;
    }
    :global(main) {
      padding: 0 !important;
    }
    .cv {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
    .cv-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 11rem 1fr;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }
    .cv-sidebar h1 {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }
    .cv-sidebar .role {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 9pt;
      margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
    }
    .cv-sidebar .role-sub {
      color: #444;
      font-size: 7.5pt;
      margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
    }
    .cv-sidebar .contact {
      font-size: 8pt;
      gap: 0.15rem;
    }
    .cv-sidebar .contact a {
      color: #1a1a1a;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .cv a {
      color: #1a1a1a;
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .cv-head {
      padding-bottom: 0.35rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }
    .cv-head h1 {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.1rem;
    }
    .cv .role,
    .cv .contact,
    .cv-head p {
      font-size: 8.5pt;
    }
    .cv section {
      margin: 0.3rem 0;
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }
    .cv h2 {
      margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
      font-size: 8pt;
    }
    .cv .projects, .cv .other {
      gap: 0.3rem;
    }
    .cv .projects li {
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }
    .cv .projects h3 {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.05rem;
    }
    .cv .project-meta {
      color: #444;
      margin-bottom: 0.1rem;
      font-size: 7.5pt;
    }
    .cv .projects p {
      margin-bottom: 0.05rem;
    }
    .cv .projects strong {
      color: #444;
      font-size: 6.5pt;
    }
    .cv .projects li p:nth-child(3),
    .cv .projects li p:nth-child(4) {
      display: inline;
    }
    .cv .projects li p:nth-child(3)::after {
      content: " · ";
      color: #444;
      padding: 0 0.15rem;
    }
    .cv .projects li p:nth-child(5) {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 0.15rem;
    }
    .cv .job {
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }
    .cv .job h3 {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.05rem;
    }
    .cv .job-meta {
      color: #444;
      margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
      font-size: 7.5pt;
    }
    .cv .role {
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
      padding-left: 0.35rem;
      border-left-color: #ccc;
    }
    .cv .role h4 {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.05rem;
      gap: 0.3rem;
    }
    .cv .role-dates {
      color: #444;
      font-size: 7.5pt;
    }
    .cv .role ul {
      gap: 0.05rem;
    }
    .cv .role li {
      padding-left: 0.6rem;
    }
    .cv .role li::before {
      color: #444;
    }
    .cv .job:last-child,
    .cv .projects li:last-child,
    .cv .role:last-child,
    .cv .edu:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .cv .skill-list li:not(:last-child)::after {
      color: #444;
    }
    .cv .edu {
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }
    .cv .edu h3 {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
